'''高粱属'''大约包含30[[种|种]]，属于[[禾本科|禾本科]]中{{le|和黍亞科|Panicoideae}}的{{le|鬚芒草族|Andropogoneae}}，广泛分布在全球各地，原产于[[热带|热带]]和[[亚热带|亚热带]]地区。大部份的品種是[[澳洲|澳洲]]的原生種，有些則擴展到[[非洲|非洲]]、[[亞洲|亞洲]]、[[中美洲|中美洲]]以及[[印度洋|印度洋]]及[[太平洋三大島群|太平洋]]的一些島上<ref>[http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/417087#page/213/mode/1up Moench, Conrad. 1794.  Methodus Plantas Horti Botanici et Agri Marburgensis : a staminum situ describendi page 207] {{Wayback|url=http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/417087#page/213/mode/1up |date=20150924212329 }} in Latin</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tropicos.org/Name/40002210 |title=Tropicos, ''Sorghum'' Moench  |accessdate=2015-09-08 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305000818/http://www.tropicos.org/Name/40002210 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.efloras.org/florataxon.aspx?flora_id=2&taxon_id=130722 |title=Flora of China Vol. 22 Page 600 <big>高粱属</big> gao liang shu  ''Sorghum'' Moench, Methodus. 207. 1794 |accessdate=2015-09-08 |archive-date=2016-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161231185626/http://www.efloras.org/florataxon.aspx?flora_id=2&taxon_id=130722 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.efloras.org/florataxon.aspx?flora_id=5&taxon_id=130722 |title=Flora of Pakistan, Sorghum Moench., Meth. Bot. 207. 1794 |accessdate=2015-09-08 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924161921/http://www.efloras.org/florataxon.aspx?flora_id=5&taxon_id=130722 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://luirig.altervista.org/flora/taxa/floraspecie.php?genere=sorghum Altervista Flora Italiana, genere ''Sorghum''] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150201021459/http://luirig.altervista.org/flora/taxa/floraspecie.php?genere=Sorghum |date=2015-02-01 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://bie.ala.org.au/species/urn:lsid:biodiversity.org.au:apni.taxon:420835 |title=Atlas of Living Australia |access-date=2015-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305085726/http://bie.ala.org.au/species/urn:lsid:biodiversity.org.au:apni.taxon:420835 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

高粱属中一個品种为[[粮食|粮食]]作物，大部分品种主要用于牧草。高粱属可栽培在世界很多溫帶氣候的地區，也可以在許多地方自然生長<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://bonap.net/NAPA/TaxonMaps/Genus/County/Sorghum |title=Biota of North America Program 2013 county distribution maps |accessdate=2015-09-08 |archive-date=2015-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150224193407/http://bonap.net/NAPA/TaxonMaps/Genus/County/Sorghum |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 栽培和利用 ==
高粱属中的一個種[[高粱|二色高粱]]（Sorghum bicolor）,<ref>{{Cite journal
|doi = 10.1007/s10722-009-9466-7
|volume = 57
|issue = 2
|pages = 243–253
|last = Mutegi
|first = Evans
|coauthors = Fabrice Sagnard, Moses Muraya, Ben Kanyenji, Bernard Rono, Caroline Mwongera, Charles Marangu, Joseph Kamau, Heiko Parzies, Santie de Villiers, Kassa Semagn, Pierre Traoré, Maryke Labuschagne
|title = Ecogeographical distribution of wild, weedy and cultivated Sorghum bicolor (L.) Moench in Kenya: implications for conservation and crop-to-wild gene flow
|journal = Genetic Resources and Crop Evolution
|accessdate = 2010-08-02
|date = 2010-02-01
}}</ref>是非洲的原生種，現在有許多馴化的品種<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.efloras.org/florataxon.aspx?flora_id=2&taxon_id=200026333 |title=bicolor |accessdate=2015-09-08 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303224620/http://www.efloras.org/florataxon.aspx?flora_id=2&taxon_id=200026333 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，高粱是全世界重要的作物，用於[[食物|食物]]（穀類及[[糖高粱|糖高粱]]）、[[饲料|饲料]]、[[牧草|牧草]]、酿[[酒|酒]]及[[生物燃料|生物燃料]]等。許多品種的高粱是{{le|耐旱|xerophyte}}及耐熱的作物，在[[乾旱|乾旱]]地區是窮人及鄉村居民的[[主食|主食]]。<!--These varieties form important components of pastures in many tropical regions.-->二色高粱是在[[热带|热带]][[草原|草原]]是非常重要的组成部分，在[[非洲|非洲]]、[[中美|中美]]和[[南亚|南亚]]也是最重要的粮食作物，在全世界的粮食生产中占第五位。<ref>[http://www.grains.org/sorghum Sorghum] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100823004012/http://www.grains.org/sorghum |date=2010-08-23 }}, U.S. Grains Council.</ref>

其中一种品种[[石茅|石茅]](''Sorghum halepense'')被[[美国农业部|美国农业部]]认定为美国的[[入侵物种|入侵物种]]<ref>[http://www.invasivespeciesinfo.gov/plants/johnsongrass.shtml Johnson Grass] {{Wayback|url=http://www.invasivespeciesinfo.gov/plants/johnsongrass.shtml |date=20090507062325 }}, U.S. Department of Agriculture, Accessed 2257 UDT, 12 March, 2009.</ref>

有的品种秸杆外皮可以编制席子，有的品种[[糖高粱|糖高粱]]秸杆含糖，可以制作糖浆，[[印度|印度]]实验将其糖分转化为[[酒精|酒精]]燃料，<ref>[http://www.agribusinessweek.com/sweet-sorghum-a-new-smart-biofuel-crop/ Sweet Sorghum : A New "Smart Biofuel Crop"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150527004827/http://www.agribusinessweek.com/sweet-sorghum-a-new-smart-biofuel-crop/ |date=2015-05-27 }} AgriBusinessWeek, 30 June 2008</ref>美国正在寻找能将其秸杆和[[叶子|叶子]]转化为酒精燃料的最佳品种<ref>[http://agnewsarchive.tamu.edu/dailynews/stories/FUEL/Oct0107a.htm Ceres and Texas A&M to Develop and Market High-Biomass Sorghum for Biofuels] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080724231547/http://agnewsarchive.tamu.edu/dailynews/stories/FUEL/Oct0107a.htm |date=2008-07-24 }} Texas A&M University System Agriculture Program, 1 October 2007</ref>。

有些高粱屬的植物在成長初期會含有高量的[[氰化氫|氰化氫]]、{{le|大麦芽碱|hordenine}}或是其他對食草動物有毒的硝酸鹽。在生長後期，若遇到乾旱或是酷熱，高粱也會含有大量的氰化物或有毒的硝酸鹽<ref>Cyanide (prussic acid) and nitrate in sorghum crops - managing the risks. Primary industries and fisheries. Queensland Government. {{cite web |url=http://www.dpi.qld.gov.au/4790_20318.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-09-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120319020718/http://www.dpi.qld.gov.au/4790_20318.htm |archivedate=2012-03-19 }}. 21 April 2011.</ref>。

在[[中国|中国]]，[[高粱|高粱]]是最好的酿造[[白酒|白酒]]的原料，所製成的酒稱為[[高粱酒|高粱酒]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://event.ttl-eshop.com.tw/lt/about/01main.aspx?cateid=129 |title=高粱酒簡介 |accessdate=2015-09-08 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304102208/http://event.ttl-eshop.com.tw/lt/about/01main.aspx?cateid=129 |dead-url=no }}</ref>或白乾。

